<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge">
  <title>{{title}}</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="/img/weather.png">
  <!-- 구글웹폰트 -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Nanum+Gothic|Nanum+Myeongjo|Noto+Serif+KR&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <!-- 폰트아이콘 라이브러리 -->
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.9.0/css/all.min.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
  <!-- jQuery -->
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.4.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="js/main.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
  {{>header}}

  <div id="main">
    <div id="main-visual">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>COFFEEFREE All that Time</h2>
        <p>당신을 일상을 풍요롭게 하는 최고의 커피를 바로 이곳에서 맛보세요!</p>
        <a href="#" class="btn-more">더보기</a>
      </div><!-- end contaier-->
    </div>

    <section id="brand">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>Special Coffee Brand</h2>
        <p>뜻한 내려온 충분히 있는 있다. 청춘은 피어나기 얼마나 부패뿐이다. 천지는 몸이 역사를 이상의 있는가? 봄바람을 가장 천자만홍이 이 그것은 바로 보라. 크고 노년에게서 방지하는 못할 시들어
          철환하였는가? 목숨이 그들을 청춘은 않는 타오르고 것은 사막이다.</p>
        {{!-- <ul>
          {{#each weather_status}}
          <li>{{city}}: {{weather}}</li>
          {{/each}}
          </ul> --}}
        <ul class="product">
          {{#each data.product}}
          <li>
            <img src={{img_url}} alt="">
            <span class="name">{{title}}</span>
            <div class="price">
              <strong>{{price}}원</strong>
              {{#if origin_price}}
              <del>{{origin_price}}원</del>
              {{/if}}
            </div>
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>

    </section>

    <section id="banner">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="coffe-product">
          <h3>Coffe Product</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="contact-us">
          <h3>Contact us</h3>
        </div>
      </div><!-- end container -->
    </section>

    <section id="sns">
      <div class="container">
        <h2>SNS</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#"><img src="http://placeimg.com/240/240/1" alt="1"></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"><img src="http://placeimg.com/240/240/2" alt="2"></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"><img src="http://placeimg.com/240/240/3" alt="3"></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"><img src="http://placeimg.com/240/240/4" alt="4"></a></li>
          <li><a href="#"><img src="http://placeimg.com/240/240/5" alt="5"></a></li>
        </ul>
      </div><!-- end container -->
    </section>

    <section id="post">
      <div class="container">
        {{#each (limit data.post 2)}}
        <article>
          <img src={{img_url}} alt="">
          <h2>{{title}}</h2>
          <p>{{text}}</p>
          <a href="#" class="btn-more">더보기</a>
        </article>
        {{/each}}
      </div><!-- end container -->
    </section>
  </div><!-- end main -->

  {{>footer}}
</body>

</html>